## Deck format

A flashcards deck is stored in the custom kronomi
config format and it looks like this:

> session = Int # in range [1, 32]
  cards = [
      {
          bucket   = Int, # in range [0, 5]
          question = String,
          answer   = String,
      },
      {
          bucket   = 3,
          question = "How are you?"
          answer   = "Very good!",
      },
      ...
  ]
